        <item>
            <title>【现场评测】Sony INZONE Buds 电竞蓝牙耳机，香港售价 + USB 插头驳 PS5、电脑、手机超低延迟</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/sony-inzone-buds/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-inzone-buds</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/sony-inzone-buds/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 11:31:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony INZONE Buds]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198689</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony INZONE Buds 今日在香港发布，它是一个专门为电子游戏而设的无线蓝牙耳机。过往讲到电竞耳机，大家只会联想到是头戴式设计的大牛龟耳机，在夏天打机往往会出一身大汗，而今次 Sony 发布的是他们首个真・无线入耳式电竞耳机，无拘无束之余，又可得到低延迟声音传送的优点。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0094.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Sony INZONE Buds 真・无线耳机，采用入耳式设计，基本上同大家听歌用的蓝牙耳机例如 WF-1000XM5 无异。而最大分别就是它附设了一个超薄的小型 USB 手指，插在 PlayStation 5、PC、智能手机的 USB-C 插口上，直接利用 2.4GHz 无线讯号来传输声音讯号。特点是相对蓝牙而言，2.4GHz 无线讯号可做到更低延迟，跟头戴式耳机一样做到低于 30ms 的延迟率，非常适合玩 FPS、TPS 游戏。而且接驳方便，毋须配对，只要一插到手机／平板／电脑／游戏机就可以听到歌、打机。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198697" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0008-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198700" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0104.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198701" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0108.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳机内置有无线降噪功能，可消除周遭噪音。收音方面，亦可用到 AI 降噪功能，消除外界噪音做到更清晰的语音通话。</p><p>而除了用 USB-C 手指之外，Sony INZONE Buds 支援了蓝牙 LE Audio 与支援此功能的智能手机、装置无线连接。目前支援蓝牙 LE Audio 的手机有 Xperia 1 IV、Xperia 5 IV，连接到这些手机，就毋须用 USB-C 手指，都可拥有超低延迟的打机音响体验。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198698" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0009-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>如果是未有支援 LE Audio 的智能手机，你可尝试插上 USB 手指到智能手机。例如 iPhone 15，小编就尝试过插上手指后可直接收听 iPhone 上的声音。</p><p>小编就尝试连接 PS5，只要把 USB-C 手指插进游戏机，戴上耳机后就马上听到游戏机声音，完全毋须配对。试玩《Call of Duty: Vanguard》可听到四方八面传来的枪声，在小型耳机上都可做到精准定位。将 USB-C 手指插到电脑，就可即时收听电脑声响。在电脑上你可配合 INZONE Hub 软件使用，获得 360 Spatial Sound for Gaming 环绕声效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198705" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0127.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198706" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0120.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲USB-C 手指直接插上 PS5 主机</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0118.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>但大家也要留意 Sony INZONE Buds 不支援 Bluetooth 蓝牙连接，在一些没有 USB-C 支援的装置如 iPhone 14 或以前的 iPhone，就要透过转接器才可听歌／打机。</p><p>价格：HK$1,590</p><p>发售日期：10 月 11 日</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198702" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0109.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0112.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>同场加映：Sony INZONE H5 电竞无线耳机</h2><p>Sony INZONE H5 是最新款的中阶电竞无线耳机，价位只为 HK$1,190。耳机净重仅为 260g，比之前 H7 的 325g 大为轻巧，但采用与 INZONE H7 同一样的耳棉，确保长时间佩戴都同样舒适。耳机同样以 USB-A 手指连接 PS5、电脑，透过 2.4GHz 无线讯号传输音讯，可做到极低的延迟。耳机充满电后最多可用到 28 小时，就算耳机无电，只要快速充电 10 分钟可获得 3 小时的续航力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198707" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0134.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198708" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0136.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198709" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0138.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>耳机机身设有 Game/Chat Balance 拨杆，可直接控制游戏／聊天声量的平衡，确保你队友的声音不会被游戏声遮盖。耳机也支援了 3.5mm 有线连接，就算耳机无电，都可马上驳线到电脑。</p><p>价格：HK$1,190</p><p>发售日期：10 月 11 日</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198692" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0037-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198693" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3-768x510.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0027-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198694" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-694x469.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="469" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-694x469.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2-768x519.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0028-2.jpg 1143w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>同场加映：Sony ECM-S1 无线咪高风</h2><p>今日 Sony ECM-S1 无线咪高风出现在铜锣湾 Sony 门市。这支咪高风可无线连接到你的 Sony 相机，适合串流直播用家使用。麦克风机身小巧轻便，配备三个 14 毫米大直径麦克风元件，可捕捉自然人声。音讯透过无线连接直接收录到摄影机，在直播过程中不会出现声音和影像分开输入时有机会出现的「声音和影像延迟」问题。</p><p>价格：HK$2,990</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198691" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0117.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
