        <item>
            <title>iOS 17.1 新功能避免误按「动作按钮」　防止 iPhone 15 在裤袋中误开电筒、相机　</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/11/ios-17-1-prevent-action-button-press-unintentionally/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 10:37:21 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Action Button]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[动作按钮]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198608</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>iPhone 15 Pro 系列将旧有的静音拨杆变成了一个叫「动作按钮」的多功能按钮。用家可自订不同功能到此按钮，除静音外，亦可设置长按启动相机、电筒等。不过有用家发现在裤袋内经常错误地按压了这个按钮，带来不便。iOS 17.1 Beta 3 就开始引入一个全新功能，避免相关事件发生。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/customize-action-button-on-iphone-15-pro-and-15-pro-max.jpg 730w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>iPhone 15 Pro 系列开始引入的「动作按钮」，可以自订不同功能，例如相机、电筒、静音、我专注模式、录音、放大镜、捷径等，用户长按这个按钮，就可直接启动已设置好的功能。不过有用家表示，即使要长按「动作按钮」才会触发相关功能，但电话放入裤袋后仍然经常误按这个「动作按钮」，以致在裤袋内经常误开相机、电筒，大量耗用手机电量。</p><p>在 iOS 17.1 Beta 3 中，将加入自动感应功能，如感应到 iPhone 被放在口袋里，长按「动作按钮」也不会触发到用家当初设置的功能，如相机、电筒等。</p><p>但用户也要留意，新机制只能防止「动作按钮」被误按。开启了画面，在锁机画面上的相机、电筒按钮，目前仍没有方法防止误按。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53-382x580.jpg" alt="" width="382" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53-382x580.jpg 382w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53-593x900.jpg 593w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53-768x1165.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53-1012x1536.jpg 1012w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-11-16.49.53.jpg 1036w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 382px" /></a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2023/10/10/ios-17-1-action-button-tweak/">MacRumors</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
